[ProMED-mail thanks Steve Berger for providing these background data, which underline that angiostrongylus is endemic in snails and human infections depend on the habit of eating raw snails. - Mod.EP

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1ob5.]
